author: 滇西小哥 Dianxi Xiaoge
description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

This is an impulsive, stream-of-consciousness episode — different from what I had imagined. It may not be filled with optimism or grand ambitions, just fragments of how I genuinely feel right now.
I’m deeply grateful to myself for surviving one “winter” after another, and even more grateful to you for walking with me through year after year of spring, summer, autumn, and winter.
In the new year, I hope we can all stay safe and happy.

Hello, everyone! I am Dianxi Xiaoge, a Yunnan native. If you enjoy my videos, please keep subscribing to my channel. I'll continue to share my life and Yunnan-styled food in my uploads. Wish you have a happy life and enjoy tasty food every day
